graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks Component<br/>Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies - Base OS and Runtimes
    UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com<br/>Required]
    CUDA[CUDA Base Images<br/>CUDA 12.6/12.8/13.0<br/>Required for GPU workbenches]
    ROCM[ROCM Base Images<br/>ROCM 6.2/6.3/6.4<br/>Required for AMD GPU]

    %% External Dependencies - IDE and ML Frameworks
    JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4<br/>Required for Jupyter images]
    PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>Required for PyTorch images]
    TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x<br/>Required for TensorFlow images]
    RStudioPkg[RStudio Server<br/>Required for RStudio images]
    CodeServerPkg[code-server<br/>Required for CodeServer images]

    %% External Dependencies - Tools
    OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI oc<br/>mirror.openshift.com<br/>Required]
    Pandoc[Pandoc<br/>Required for PDF export]
    TexLive[TeX Live<br/>Required for LaTeX rendering]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController[odh-notebook-controller<br/>Deploys workbench pods]
    Dashboard[odh-dashboard<br/>UI for image selection]
    KubeflowPipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines Elyra<br/>Uses runtime images]
    OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy<br/>Sidecar authentication]
    PVC[Persistent Volume Claims<br/>User data storage]
    Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>External access]

    %% External Services at Runtime
    PyPI[pypi.org<br/>Runtime package installation]
    Quay[quay.io<br/>Image registry]
    RedHatReg[registry.redhat.io<br/>RHOAI images]
    S3[S3 Storage<br/>User data optional]
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>kubectl/oc commands]

    %% Build Dependencies
    Konflux[Konflux CI/CD<br/>Automated builds]

    %% External OS/Runtime Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI9
    Notebooks -->|GPU acceleration| CUDA
    Notebooks -->|AMD GPU acceleration| ROCM
    Notebooks -->|IDE framework| JupyterLab
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow
    Notebooks -->|R IDE| RStudioPkg
    Notebooks -->|VS Code IDE| CodeServerPkg
    Notebooks -->|cluster CLI| OpenShiftCLI
    Notebooks -->|document conversion| Pandoc
    Notebooks -->|LaTeX rendering| TexLive

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|deploys using| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|displays| Notebooks
    KubeflowPipelines -->|executes| Notebooks
    OAuthProxy -.->|protects| Notebooks
    PVC -.->|mounts to| Notebooks
    Routes -.->|exposes| Notebooks

    %% Runtime dependencies (dashed - used by running workbenches)
    Notebooks -.->|installs from| PyPI
    Notebooks -.->|loads data from| S3
    Notebooks -.->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Notebooks -.->|pulled from| Quay
    Notebooks -.->|pulled from| RedHatReg

    %% Build dependencies
    Konflux -->|builds| Notebooks
    Konflux -->|publishes to| Quay
    Konflux -->|publishes to| RedHatReg

